    {
      "id": "PopularPost378451",
      "post_content": "The problem with this card is Radiance as a mechanic. Not only is it really weak in a Boros vs. Boros mirror match, but it is also horrible in a set where there is so much multicolor going on. The chances that you end up hitting your own creatures with removal, or boosting your opponents' creatures, makes it unreliable when something as awesome as [Lightning Helix](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Helix) exists in the same set. Targeted removal and targeted buffs are much more reliable than something that has a chance to backfire and harm you. There are also plenty of effects that boost your own forces and not your opponents'.  \n  \nThis card in particular reminds me of [Magnify](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Magnify). It can potentially boost everybody, making it sometimes a win-more card which is only helpful if you already have more creatures, in which case you will probably win anyway through numbers. At best, it's a cheap [Warrior's Honor](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Warrior's Honor) or the like. Here are some examples of better cards with comp... [(see all)](javascript:void(0);)",
      "posted_by": "Equinox523",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost378451\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_post\">The problem with this card is Radiance as a mechanic.  Not only is it really weak in a Boros vs. Boros mirror match, but it is also horrible in a set where there is so much multicolor going on.  The chances that you end up hitting your own creatures with removal, or boosting your opponents' creatures, makes it unreliable when something as awesome as <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Lightning Helix\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Helix\">Lightning Helix</a> exists in the same set.  Targeted removal and targeted buffs are much more reliable than something that has a chance to backfire and harm you.  There are also plenty of effects that boost your own forces and not your opponents'.<br/><br/>This card in particular reminds me of <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Magnify\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Magnify\">Magnify</a>.  It can potentially boost everybody, making it sometimes a win-more card which is only helpful if you already have more creatures, in which case you will probably win anyway through numbers.  At best, it's a cheap <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Warrior's Honor\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Warrior's Honor\">Warrior's Honor</a> or the like.  Here are some examples of better cards with comp... <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" onclick=\"ExpandPost(event, this, 378451)\">(see all)</a></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '378451'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy1136\">Equinox523</span>\r\n                                (6/4/2014 10:14:37 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>"
